v   1.0  0.0  -1.0
v   1.0  2.0  -1.0
v  -1.0  2.0  -1.0

g backWall
usemtl mirror
f -4 -3 -2 -1

## Object frontwall
v  -1.0  0.0  1.0
v   1.0  0.0  1.0
v   1.0  2.0  1.0
v  -1.0  2.0  1.0

g frontWall
usemtl mirror
f -1 -2 -3 -4

